"""
Edwin Systems Health Report -- nightly diagnostics + cost tracking.

Generates a markdown report covering:
  1. API costs (daily + MTD)
  2. Pipeline health (connector freshness + job failure streaks)
  3. Commitment aging
  4. Memory validity (bi-temporal audit)
  5. Vector store health (Qdrant) + retrieval-quality eval
  6. Knowledge graph health (Neo4j)
  7. Indexer status (context coverage)
  8. Infrastructure (Docker / Ollama)

Usage:
    report                    # Generate and publish to briefing book
    report --stdout            # Print to stdout instead
    report --date 2026-04-03  # Report for a specific date
"""

